roup relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-red-400/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-400/10 border border-red-400/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-cyan-400/30 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-down w-5 h-5 text-red-400 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 17h6v-6\"></path><path d=\"m22 17-8.5-8.5-5 5L2 7\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black mb-3 leading-snug\">Outdated websites kill trust</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed\">First impressions happen in seconds. Legacy sites signal instability and drive high-value prospects straight to competitors.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card glass-card-hover rounded-3xl p-8 group relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-red-400/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-400/10 border border-red-400/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-cyan-400/30 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock w-5 h-5 text-red-400 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black mb-3 leading-snug\">Manual workflows waste time</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Teams spend hours on repetitive tasks that should be automated — draining productivity and slowing every decision.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card glass-card-hover rounded-3xl p-8 group relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-red-400/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-400/10 border border-red-400/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-cyan-400/30 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert w-5 h-5 text-red-400 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-black mb-3 leading-snug\">Poor systems block growth</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Fragmented tools and disconnected data create bottlenecks that cap revenue and make scaling nearly impossible.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card glass-card-hover rounded-3xl p-8 group relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-red-400/30 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-red-400/10 border border-red-400/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:border-cyan-400/30 transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap-off w-5 h-5 text-red-400 group-hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors\" aria-hidden=\"